\f0\b Primary Goal:
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Build a modern, local-first, AI-ready, extensible personal productivity and work management platform that combines task management, project management, scheduling, planning, knowledge management, automation, and AI assistance into a single unified ecosystem.\
Unlike traditional task managers (Todoist, TickTick, Microsoft To Do, Things, etc.), Project Sentinel is being designed as an intelligent planning engine capable of understanding relationships between work items rather than simply storing lists.\
