\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Long-Term Vision\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Project Sentinel is intended to become a comprehensive personal operating system for work and life management. Rather than functioning as another task list, it will serve as an intelligent decision-support platform that combines task execution, planning, scheduling, automation, analytics, and AI assistance.\
By leveraging structured task relationships, dependencies, recurrence, priorities, and contextual information, Sentinel will evolve into a system capable of proactively guiding users toward their most impactful work while remaining extensible through plugins and integrations. The long-term objective is to create a local-first, privacy-conscious platform that can rival or surpass commercial productivity suites while remaining fully under the user's control.\
This serves as a solid project record. As the project grows, you can maintain it as a living 
\f2\fs26 PROJECT_HISTORY.md
\f1\fs24  or 
\f2\fs26 ARCHITECTURE.md
\f1\fs24  document in the repository and update it at the end of each milestone.\
